    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Solution solution = new Solution();

        // Example 1: n = 27
        System.out.println(solution.isPowerOfThree(27)); // true

        // Example 2: n = 0
        System.out.println(solution.isPowerOfThree(0)); // false

        // Example 3: n = -1
        System.out.println(solution.isPowerOfThree(-1)); // false
    }
}
```

### Follow-up: Without Loops/Recursion

This solution already meets the requirement of not using loops or recursion. It leverages the mathematical property of logarithms to determine if a number is a power of three.

